LET'S TAKE THIS THING
FOR A SPIN, ALREADY.
STEP
Sit back, relax, and find your happy place. Hint: it's in the touch
screen right in front of you. To channel surf with ease, lift up the
lid on your armrest and pull out a remote control of your very
own. It's on a retractable cord for when you're done with it.
One side of your remote has TV/movie controls. Flip it over to
find a QWERTY keyboard and video game controls. Your remote
is the best way to interact with Red.
To make a purchase from
our onboard shop or cafe,
just swipe your card on the
bottom of the screen.
001
HIFT
To type one of the special
characters in blue, hold down
the button with the blue dot
while pressing the character
you want to enter.
Example: blue dot + X = @

STEP 2
If you're touchy-feely, you can also use the touch screen
to interact with Red. Just be sure to tap lightly with your
fingertip so as not to disturb the guest in front of you.
INSIDER TIP
Hungry, but can't take your eyes
off the TV? Tap "eat," and you can order while
watching your riveting program. Now that's
multitasking.
While you're at it, treat a travel
companion to something
delicious using our Seat-to-Seat
Delivery feature. Just select
another seat when you order a
drink, meal, or snack, and we'll
deliver it directly.
@*#!
00000000E
@VIRGINAMERICA
STEP 3
For travelers who like to bring their own toys, let's make a connection.
Will it be power or USB? Plugs are located between the seats in each row,
just below the cushions. Remember to plug in before your battery runs out.
